// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0425 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: b3b8bd29-f812-50d7-a1b4-f03115255351

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*alpine:3.4*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
